Interface OutbreakTemporalState

All Superinterfaces:
Abstraction.TemporalState<Outbreak>, Cloneable, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
OutbreakHistory, OutbreakState
All Known Implementing Classes:
ImmutableOutbreakHistory, ImmutableOutbreakState
public interface OutbreakTemporalState extends Abstraction.TemporalState<Outbreak>, Cloneable
Any data related to the state of the outbreak which is valid only in a specific time point. This list of things is shared between the OutbreakState and OutbreakHistory
